    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314450/extras/72c911dbe9b11ce43dc62a5d61add907.poster.avif?t=1733600819\" width=800 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314450/extras/72c911dbe9b11ce43dc62a5d61add907.webm?t=1733600819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314450/extras/72c911dbe9b11ce43dc62a5d61add907.mp4?t=1733600819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>The honeypot murders</strong> is a point-and-click adventure game that takes place in a colorful world inspired by mid-century cartoons. In this version of America, honey has been outlawed. You play as Arthur, a dim-witted drivers-ed teacher with a heroic sweet tooth. His friend and honey-dealer has gone missing and it is up to him to find out what happened.<br><br><strong><u>STORY</u></strong><br>America has banned all sugar products, but that hasn't stopped some resourceful individuals from creating a blackmarket, filled with beekeepers, molasses brewers, and other unsavory individuals. Arthur must delve into this seedy underworld to find his missing friend...and maybe score a jar or two of honey for his troubles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314450/extras/1007bc16dbee26a3c93a8a55bfdfb48e.poster.avif?t=1733600819\" width=800 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314450/extras/1007bc16dbee26a3c93a8a55bfdfb48e.webm?t=1733600819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314450/extras/1007bc16dbee26a3c93a8a55bfdfb48e.mp4?t=1733600819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u><strong>FEATURES</strong></u><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Lie to strangers! <br></li><li>Steal all the honey!<br></li><li>Throw rotten apples at security guards!<br></li><li>Hand drawn!<br></li><li>Hand animated!<br></li><li>Fully voiced!<br></li><li>Fleshed out world to explore!<br></li><li>Cast of bizarre characters!<br></li><li>Chock full of puzzles and mysteries to solve!</li></ul>",
